{"tid":611111,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"發夢夢到個電話號碼(4)","createTime":"2018-03-30T15:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T14:04:24.000Z","uid":142433,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bc043d6534ee4044d1a43c42681fac968aea9a7a","tid":611111,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"Post1:［懸疑］發夢夢到個電話號碼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/163062/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/163062/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\nPost2: 發夢夢到個電話號碼(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/163541/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/163541/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\nPost3: 發夢夢到個電話號碼(3)-報料上東張西望好冇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/167208/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/167208/page/1?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"26f5e259c07be99d73b7d4abd9e5789037a784f7","tid":611111,"uid":142433,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:38:13.000Z","msg":"事源：事主指日前朋友夢中遇見一男子，該男子要求事主致電21831120給他<br />\n惟事主與朋友及眾多網友經過多翻驗證及測試，發現電話有以下數項特徵及疑點。<br />\n<br />\n1. 該號碼在打岀後對方立即接通<br />\n2. 該號碼可同時接收多個電話<br />\n3. 對方以固定頻率發岀「督，督」聲響，但亦有網友試後指聲響非固定<br />\n4. 聲音頻率未確認是否屬於摩斯密碼，但節奏均勻，固機會較微<br />\n5. 電話曾傳出懷疑呼吸聲、懷疑咳嗽聲、風聲、海浪聲、雀仔聲、飛機升降聲、腳踏聲、懷疑有人講話但十分模糊（需要佩戴耳機並調高音量，否則難會較難分辨雜聲）<br />\n6.號碼頭四位數經調查後疑似位於大嶼山電話，加上網友於電話聽到疑似飛機升降聲，認為電話位於香港國際機場<br />\n7.2183+任何號碼(尾四位數)都會立刻接通並傳出同樣聲音<br />\n8. 有於機場工作網友曾嘗試以機場內線致電但卻未能打岀，反以外線則成功，固此懷疑該電話並非屬於機場內部<br />\n9. 根據拒收訊息登記冊顯示，該號碼於2013-06-19登記，故該電話應有持有人或團體<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多<br />\n歡迎各位巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6520d74e1539fd6711dc98d45380add0f93399c","tid":611111,"uid":45352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"又來過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來已經成年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855b6c829187656ccc5d15a1b71f43ba746438f8","tid":611111,"uid":142433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d6520d74e1539fd6711dc98d45380add0f93399c","tid":611111,"uid":45352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"又來過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來已經成年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"要搵出真相"},{"pid":"8319107b6dee8a3bcf9e0afccf0d89d20d7f94fb","tid":611111,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"又推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adab246b62e0630f99b23aef3bf3a5cfc9ab24eb","tid":611111,"uid":142433,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:47:33.000Z","msg":"岩岩再打去一次 大約6分鐘有呼氣聲"},{"pid":"ac6e7b517e3542e837a2b19d384382ec77b7b88c","tid":611111,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dfc62121b26ad166d4c039231cbb73e7010b589","tid":611111,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"又黎"},{"pid":"586225476ca1010e8b86fa22f3864972ea507510","tid":611111,"uid":135577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"6b83639f1fe7d2f04500140666e0452944c932f4","tid":611111,"uid":60936,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"全靠澳洲sms post令呢個post又再推返"},{"pid":"c61056b082db35bd9b8a23514f44ca631b77d4bf","tid":611111,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"81028332"},{"pid":"51c7391066fd3744ccd77789bda02072784703f7","tid":611111,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,